description: Lubegard Automatic Transmission Fluid Protectant helps to prevent the failure of transmissions, since 9 out of 10 transmissions usually fail due to the heat. For every 10 degrees of heat reduced, Lubegard doubles the life of the transmission fluid. For every 20 degrees of heat reduced, the life of the transmission is doubled. The Lubegard automatic transmission fluid protectant prevents overheating, reducing elevated operating temperatures up to 40 degrees fahrenheit. The reason Lubegard should be chosen, is the very same reason car manufacturers, transmission technicians and the top 3 transmission repair chains do: solid test results and over a billion miles of proven performance. Lubegard's automatic transmission fluid protectant is the number one used product in the professional transmission rebuild industry, and the only product of its kind to be used, endorsed, designated and approved by multiple major automobile manufacturers. Lubegard automatic transmission fluid protectant is for use in all automatic transmissions and will absolutely reduce heat, eliminate shudders, noises, foaming, oxidation and make the transmission shift smoother.
title: Lubegard 60902 Automatic Transmission Fluid Protectant
